      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i'm trying to stay calm but i'm just really panicking now because i can't even drive myself. i don't want to bother an ambulance for what might just be bad food poisoning or something. if i just take a couple of the oxy and some tylenol it'll definitely help the pain go away so i can just rest until the sun comes up. won't the pain just die down once the meds kick in? i just need to know if it's safe to just sleep through this.",
